+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

This package has installed the American and British dictionaries.
Default dictionary has been set to `british' but can be changed using:
    ${PREFIX}/bin/ispell-config

Dictionary packages for other languages are also available.
See the output of:
    pkg_info -Q ispell
